definitions.definition: A prickling or mildly stinging sensation ; frisson .
A tingling sound; a chime or tinkle .

main_definition: A prickling or mildly stinging sensation ; frisson .
secondary_definitions: A tingling sound; a chime or tinkle .

definitions.definition: A nail of the very smallest size; a tack .
A patch that covers a hole in something that needs to be watertight , such as a roof or a boat .
An attachment in the middle of a long guide line to keep it from sagging .

main_definition: A nail of the very smallest size; a tack .
secondary_definitions: A patch that covers a hole in something that needs to be watertight , such as a roof or a boat .
( masonry ) An attachment in the middle of a long guide line to keep it from sagging .
